                  </hi>. I am pilot of the prisoner's vessel, the <hi rend="italic">Harmonica.</hi> I saw Aldridge bring some trowsers on board our vessel, and exchange them for a cap—he came afterwards, on the same day, with a coat, and sold it to the prisoner—I saw him give some money, I cannot say how much.</p>
